#AGRF2012 The government of Tanzania is committed to lifting agricultural tech schools to promising agro innovation areas.
#AGRF2012 Thanks to AGRA for the hard work and support on the efforts to achieve a food secure and prosperous Africa.
#AGRF2012 Tanzania is 95% food self sufficient but our aim is to do more, even feed our neighbours with increased investment.
#AGRF2012 We are pro-actively involving the private sector in developing agriculture & more investment in research.
#AGRF2012 Agriculture funding should not just remain the domain of government & donors but also the private sector.
#AGRF2012 Without investing in agriculture and nutrition, our goal to transform African agriculture will remain a song without dancers.
#AGRF2012 Credit financing is still critical. Our efforts focus on making financial services more responsive to smallholder farmers.
#AGRF2012 The need to scale up investment & innovation is crucial. Small African farm sizes & low yields are faced by meagre livelihoods.
